===Eytmology===
[[degree]] and [[Celsius]]

===Noun===
'''degree Celsius''' (''plural'' '''degrees Celsius''')

#A [[metric]] [[unit]] of [[temperature]], a [[derived unit]] of the [[International System of Units]].  Symbol: °C

====Usage note====
*In technical contexts, the symbol should always include the degree symbol °, as the symbol C alone is used for coulombs.  In informal usage, where the meaning is clear, the degree symbol is sometimes omitted.

